1
00:00:02,702 --> 00:00:04,938
[NARRATOR]
Wealth, fame, power...

2
00:00:04,938 --> 00:00:06,673
Gold Roger, the King
of the Pirates,

3
00:00:06,706 --> 00:00:09,509
attained this and everything
else the world had to offer.

4
00:00:09,542 --> 00:00:12,879
And his dying words drove
countless souls to the seas.

5
00:00:12,912 --> 00:00:14,547
[GOLD ROGER]
You want my treasure?

6
00:00:14,581 --> 00:00:15,615
You can have it.

7
00:00:15,682 --> 00:00:18,952
I left everything I gathered
together in one place.

8
00:00:18,952 --> 00:00:21,421
Now, you just have to find it.

9
00:00:23,289 --> 00:00:25,859
[NARRATOR] These words
lured men to the Grand Line

10
00:00:25,892 --> 00:00:27,961
in pursuit of dreams greater
than they've ever dared

11
00:00:28,028 --> 00:00:31,965
to imagine! This is the time
known as the Great Pirate Era!

12
00:00:32,432 --> 00:00:37,871
<i>♪Come aboard and bring along</i>
<i>all your hopes and dreams</i>

13
00:00:37,904 --> 00:00:43,643
<i>Together we will find everything</i>
<i>that we're looking for</i>

14
00:00:43,710 --> 00:00:45,378
<i>One Piece!</i>

15
00:00:49,916 --> 00:00:55,455
<i>Compass left behind</i>
<i>It'll only slow us down</i>

16
00:00:55,488 --> 00:00:57,657
<i>Your heart will be your guide</i>

17
00:00:57,657 --> 00:01:00,960
<i>Raise the sails</i>
<i>and take the helm</i>

18
00:01:00,994 --> 00:01:06,666
<i>That legendary place that the</i>
<i>end of the map reveals</i>

19
00:01:06,666 --> 00:01:13,473
<i>Is only legendary</i>
<i>until someone proves it real</i>

20
00:01:13,506 --> 00:01:16,476
<i>Through it all, through all</i>
<i>the troubled times,</i>

21
00:01:16,509 --> 00:01:19,012
<i>through the heartache,</i>
<i>and through the pain</i>

22
00:01:19,079 --> 00:01:24,451
<i>Know that I will be there</i>
<i>to stand by you</i>

23
00:01:24,484 --> 00:01:27,854
<i>Just like I know</i>
<i>you'll stand by me!</i>

24
00:01:27,854 --> 00:01:33,593
<i>So come aboard and bring along</i>
<i>all your hopes and dreams</i>

25
00:01:33,626 --> 00:01:39,499
<i>Together we will find everything</i>
<i>that we're looking for</i>

26
00:01:39,532 --> 00:01:45,472
<i>There's always room for you</i>
<i>if you want to be my friend</i>

27
00:01:45,505 --> 00:01:50,877
<i>We are, we are on the cruise</i>

28
00:01:50,944 --> 00:01:51,811
<i>We are!♪</i>

29
00:01:54,547 --> 00:01:58,318
Might as well throw
that gas mask away!

30
00:01:58,318 --> 00:02:02,155
You are no longer worthy
to be a Krieg Pirate.

31
00:02:04,124 --> 00:02:06,326
[KRIEG]
Die!

32
00:02:06,326 --> 00:02:10,730
[LUFFY yelling]

33
00:02:10,797 --> 00:02:13,566
[LUFFY] I'm not going to let
that happen, you bastard!

34
00:02:13,633 --> 00:02:17,170
You're wasting your
time, Chore Boy!

35
00:02:17,170 --> 00:02:19,506
[LUFFY yelping]

36
00:02:19,539 --> 00:02:21,341
[LUFFY gasps]

37
00:02:21,341 --> 00:02:23,676
[LUFFY yelling]

38
00:02:23,676 --> 00:02:29,082
[LUFFY grunting]

39
00:02:29,149 --> 00:02:31,718
[LUFFY]
Aw, crap.

40
00:02:31,751 --> 00:02:34,187
Ghin!

41
00:02:34,187 --> 00:02:37,490
You don't have to
listen to that blowhard,

42
00:02:37,524 --> 00:02:39,692
because I'm gonna
kick his ass!

43
00:02:39,726 --> 00:02:40,527
[GHIN growls]

44
00:02:40,560 --> 00:02:44,430
No! My captain
cannot be defeated.

45
00:02:44,497 --> 00:02:46,866
Don Krieg is the
strongest man alive

46
00:02:46,900 --> 00:02:49,235
and I respect his punishment.

47
00:02:49,269 --> 00:02:51,437
Will you please snap out of it?

48
00:02:51,504 --> 00:02:54,374
He's going to kill you!

49
00:02:54,407 --> 00:02:56,176
I deserve it.

50
00:02:56,209 --> 00:02:59,212
Obeying my emotions meant
betraying my captain.

51
00:02:59,245 --> 00:03:03,116
If I were in his position, then
I would've done the same thing.

52
00:03:03,183 --> 00:03:06,219
And now, death is the
only honor I have left.

53
00:03:08,288 --> 00:03:08,922
Don't!

54
00:03:08,955 --> 00:03:11,724
[SANJI grunts]
Why? No...

55
00:03:11,724 --> 00:03:15,195
Heh! So you've
remembered your place.

56
00:03:15,228 --> 00:03:17,530
But, it's much
too late for that.

57
00:03:17,564 --> 00:03:20,767
Now, you will both die together.

58
00:03:20,800 --> 00:03:22,468
It's the MH 5...

59
00:03:22,535 --> 00:03:23,403
Poison...

60
00:03:23,436 --> 00:03:24,537
Gas Bomb...

61
00:03:24,571 --> 00:03:26,406
Fire!

62
00:03:31,578 --> 00:03:32,645
[LUFFY]
"I Won't Die!

63
00:03:32,712 --> 00:03:35,715
Fierce Battle, Luffy vs. Krieg."

64
00:03:40,453 --> 00:03:41,754
[PIRATES yelling]

65
00:03:41,788 --> 00:03:43,590
[COOKS screaming]

66
00:03:43,590 --> 00:03:45,558
[PATTY]
Get inside the restaurant!

67
00:03:49,295 --> 00:03:50,597
‐‐[LUFFY] Thank you!
‐‐[PIRATES gasp]

68
00:03:50,597 --> 00:03:53,132
Sanji, Ghin, catch!

69
00:03:54,434 --> 00:03:55,635
Now, for mine.

70
00:03:55,668 --> 00:03:57,837
[LUFFY gasps]
Where'd they go?

71
00:03:57,904 --> 00:03:59,572
[LUFFY gasping]

72
00:04:03,610 --> 00:04:04,611
[gasps]

73
00:04:06,846 --> 00:04:08,448
[yelling]
Don't die!

74
00:04:08,481 --> 00:04:10,583
Don't die, don't die,
don't die, don't die!

75
00:04:10,617 --> 00:04:11,618
[LUFFY]
Huh?

76
00:04:19,659 --> 00:04:22,262
[KRIEG]
This, is power.

77
00:04:37,810 --> 00:04:39,779
[LUFFY huffs]
I'm alive!

78
00:04:39,812 --> 00:04:42,448
That mask appeared just in time.

79
00:04:48,321 --> 00:04:50,223
[COOK J]
What a crazy bastard!

80
00:04:50,290 --> 00:04:51,824
[COOK K]
He tried to kill us all.

81
00:04:51,824 --> 00:04:53,559
That guy's gotta be insane.

82
00:04:53,626 --> 00:04:55,728
[COOK L] I can't believe
he used poison gas.

83
00:04:55,795 --> 00:04:56,896
[COOK JJ]
He must be a demon.

84
00:04:56,963 --> 00:04:59,499
No human would do that.

85
00:04:59,499 --> 00:05:01,868
[BOTH growling]

86
00:05:12,011 --> 00:05:14,681
Do ya' think Sanji and
the Chore Boy made it?

87
00:05:14,681 --> 00:05:15,748
I don't know.

88
00:05:15,815 --> 00:05:18,985
Look, the poison
gas is clearing up.

89
00:05:28,828 --> 00:05:30,263
[SANJI]
Ghin!

90
00:05:33,366 --> 00:05:35,368
[SANJI]
Let go.

91
00:05:35,401 --> 00:05:37,503
You can let go now.

92
00:05:39,372 --> 00:05:40,873
Hey, Ghin, are you okay?

93
00:05:40,907 --> 00:05:44,877
[GHIN gasping]

94
00:05:44,911 --> 00:05:48,414
It's your mask...
you gave it to me.

95
00:05:48,448 --> 00:05:49,349
[GHIN groans]

96
00:05:49,382 --> 00:05:50,016
[LUFFY]
No!

97
00:05:50,049 --> 00:05:52,518
[KRIEG laughing]

98
00:05:52,552 --> 00:05:54,020
[KRIEG]
What a fool!

99
00:05:54,053 --> 00:05:58,391
You are paying for a plate
of food with your life.

100
00:05:58,391 --> 00:05:59,392
Oh, well.

101
00:05:59,392 --> 00:06:02,895
Maybe you'll learn...
when you're dead. Heh!

102
00:06:02,895 --> 00:06:07,800
[KRIEG laughing]

103
00:06:07,867 --> 00:06:08,901
That bastard.

104
00:06:08,901 --> 00:06:10,903
First he orders
Ghin to kill himself

105
00:06:10,903 --> 00:06:12,872
and then he mocks the poor guy.

106
00:06:12,905 --> 00:06:15,074
He should respect the fact
that he followed his order

107
00:06:15,074 --> 00:06:16,376
in the end.

108
00:06:16,409 --> 00:06:22,882
[labored breathng]

109
00:06:22,915 --> 00:06:24,417
Don...

110
00:06:24,417 --> 00:06:29,789
Ah! Don Krieg!

111
00:06:29,822 --> 00:06:31,457
Ghin...

112
00:06:31,491 --> 00:06:33,559
[GHIN panting]

113
00:06:35,928 --> 00:06:40,600
So, it seems...

114
00:06:40,633 --> 00:06:45,405
Don Krieg was not the right
man for you to follow, was he?

115
00:06:45,438 --> 00:06:49,008
[KRIEG laughing]

116
00:06:49,075 --> 00:06:49,976
[KRIEG]
It figures

117
00:06:50,009 --> 00:06:52,111
that you still feel for
that pathetic scum.

118
00:06:52,111 --> 00:06:52,678
[SANJI]
Scum?!

119
00:06:52,745 --> 00:06:53,646
[KRIEG]
That's right.

120
00:06:53,679 --> 00:06:56,816
Anyone who loses focus
and betrays my ship,

121
00:06:56,849 --> 00:06:58,418
is worthless to me.

122
00:06:58,451 --> 00:07:00,620
They'll almost
certainly do it again.

123
00:07:00,653 --> 00:07:02,855
Putting him out of his
misery is an act of mercy

124
00:07:02,922 --> 00:07:05,625
to keep him from dishonoring
himself in the future

125
00:07:05,658 --> 00:07:07,427
and endangering my crew.

126
00:07:07,460 --> 00:07:08,928
But... he just...

127
00:07:08,961 --> 00:07:12,098
I never thought the Captain
would kill his chief commander!

128
00:07:12,131 --> 00:07:12,799
I know!

129
00:07:12,799 --> 00:07:14,700
Ghin has been his right hand man

130
00:07:14,767 --> 00:07:16,936
for even longer than I've
been part of the crew.

131
00:07:16,969 --> 00:07:19,972
That's right, see, no one's
ever showed more loyalty

132
00:07:19,972 --> 00:07:23,042
to Don Krieg than Ghin
has over the years.

133
00:07:23,109 --> 00:07:25,511
How could he forget what
Ghin did for us after

134
00:07:25,545 --> 00:07:26,946
we escaped from the Grand Line

135
00:07:26,979 --> 00:07:28,881
and Fullbody's
Marines were after us?

136
00:07:28,948 --> 00:07:30,616
It was a miracle we escaped!

137
00:07:30,650 --> 00:07:33,619
[PIRATE J] Yeah, he was willing
to sacrifice his life for us

138
00:07:33,653 --> 00:07:35,021
by acting as a decoy.

139
00:07:35,054 --> 00:07:37,890
Without him, we wouldn't
have made it out of there.

140
00:07:37,957 --> 00:07:39,826
Ghin's laid down his
life for Don Krieg

141
00:07:39,826 --> 00:07:41,527
a hundred times, easy.

142
00:07:41,561 --> 00:07:43,396
I can't believe the
captain would kill him

143
00:07:43,463 --> 00:07:44,664
with such little care.

144
00:07:44,697 --> 00:07:48,000
[panting, coughing]

145
00:07:48,000 --> 00:07:49,569
That's so cruel.

146
00:07:49,635 --> 00:07:52,004
Patty, get the kit, hurry!

147
00:07:52,004 --> 00:07:53,639
It's for food poisoning.

148
00:07:53,673 --> 00:07:55,975
I don't think it will
work on gas, Sanji.

149
00:07:56,008 --> 00:07:57,877
I don't care! We have to try!

150
00:07:57,910 --> 00:07:59,145
Put the mask on em'.

151
00:07:59,178 --> 00:08:01,747
It will detoxify the
gas in his lungs.

152
00:08:01,814 --> 00:08:04,183
Then, bring him upstairs
and let him breathe.

153
00:08:04,217 --> 00:08:06,752
It's the only chance
we have to save him.

154
00:08:06,819 --> 00:08:09,889
[GHIN coughing]

155
00:08:11,691 --> 00:08:13,092
Patty, Carne, hurry!

156
00:08:13,159 --> 00:08:14,093
Help me!

157
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,695
[PATTY]
All right already!

158
00:08:15,728 --> 00:08:18,664
[CARNE]
Me too? All right, I'm comin'.

159
00:08:18,698 --> 00:08:20,600
Ha! It's no use.

160
00:08:20,666 --> 00:08:23,202
He's going to die
within the hour.

161
00:08:25,571 --> 00:08:27,607
[LUFFY]
Don't you dare die, Ghin.

162
00:08:27,673 --> 00:08:28,508
[gasps]

163
00:08:28,541 --> 00:08:30,543
[GHIN gasps]

164
00:08:30,576 --> 00:08:33,880
[LUFFY] You can't let
someone like him win.

165
00:08:35,581 --> 00:08:37,617
Stick around. Now, I'm mad!

166
00:08:37,683 --> 00:08:40,520
You'll wanna see what I'm
going to do to him next!

167
00:08:40,553 --> 00:08:45,925
[GHIN grunting]
You can't defeat him.

168
00:08:45,958 --> 00:08:47,026
Wait a second.

169
00:08:47,059 --> 00:08:48,895
Attacking him head on
is exactly what he wants!

170
00:08:48,895 --> 00:08:50,930
He's strongest that way.

171
00:08:53,633 --> 00:08:54,901
I'm not worried.

172
00:08:54,934 --> 00:08:55,902
[gasps]

173
00:08:55,902 --> 00:08:58,104
[LUFFY] Go ahead and
give it your best shot!

174
00:08:58,137 --> 00:08:59,372
[SANJI]
Don't!

175
00:08:59,405 --> 00:09:04,544
Dumb kid. When you lose your
patience, you become easy prey!

176
00:09:04,577 --> 00:09:07,246
You are only running toward
one thing, Chore Boy.

177
00:09:07,280 --> 00:09:09,081
And that is...

178
00:09:09,115 --> 00:09:09,782
He's dead.

179
00:09:09,815 --> 00:09:10,883
Really dead.

180
00:09:10,917 --> 00:09:12,251
... your funeral.

181
00:09:12,251 --> 00:09:13,786
[LUFFY]
My funeral?

182
00:09:19,258 --> 00:09:21,127
Oh, no, get out of there!

183
00:09:23,996 --> 00:09:25,231
He got hit!

184
00:09:30,002 --> 00:09:32,238
He's done!

185
00:09:32,271 --> 00:09:33,773
Poor guy.

186
00:09:36,676 --> 00:09:37,777
[KRIEG]
Huh...

187
00:09:38,911 --> 00:09:41,113
[LUFFY]
Gum‐Gum...

188
00:09:41,113 --> 00:09:42,515
Heh... C'mon!

189
00:09:42,582 --> 00:09:43,115
The spikes!

190
00:09:43,115 --> 00:09:43,649
Here we go!

191
00:09:43,683 --> 00:09:45,918
[KRIEG]
Just try it!

192
00:09:45,952 --> 00:09:47,520
He's got no place to hit!

193
00:09:49,689 --> 00:09:52,959
[LUFFY]
... Pistol!

194
00:09:52,992 --> 00:09:55,027
Ah! No!

195
00:10:01,834 --> 00:10:06,772
[KRIEG groans]

196
00:10:22,788 --> 00:10:25,291
[LUFFY grunts]

197
00:10:25,324 --> 00:10:26,692
[PIRATES chattering]

198
00:10:26,726 --> 00:10:27,960
[PIRATE Z]
Don Krieg is down!

199
00:10:27,960 --> 00:10:29,562
That punk got him!

200
00:10:29,629 --> 00:10:31,664
[PIRATE J]
What is that kid, anyway?

201
00:10:31,697 --> 00:10:34,834
He punched him right
through the spikes!

202
00:10:38,804 --> 00:10:40,640
[PIRATE Z]
That's messed up!

203
00:10:40,640 --> 00:10:42,008
[PIRATE J]
I've never seen him get hit

204
00:10:42,041 --> 00:10:45,511
in any kind of fight, ever!

205
00:10:45,544 --> 00:10:47,813
[PIRATE A] He busted right
through that porcupine cape

206
00:10:47,847 --> 00:10:49,649
and smashed him
right in the face!

207
00:10:49,682 --> 00:10:52,018
[PIRATE Z]
I... I can't believe it!

208
00:10:58,891 --> 00:11:02,662
[LUFFY grunts]
So, is this my funeral?

209
00:11:02,662 --> 00:11:04,830
Or yours?

210
00:11:04,830 --> 00:11:06,499
You can't kill me...

211
00:11:06,532 --> 00:11:10,736
[LUFFY grunts]
...with little spikes!

212
00:11:10,770 --> 00:11:13,873
My funeral...

213
00:11:13,906 --> 00:11:17,343
[LUFFY grunts]
...will take more than this!

214
00:11:17,376 --> 00:11:19,779
[LUFFY pants]

215
00:11:29,689 --> 00:11:33,526
[LUFFY] You'll have to
do better than that...

216
00:11:33,559 --> 00:11:35,895
...if you wanna beat me.

217
00:11:38,631 --> 00:11:41,967
Because I don't think its
time for me to die, just yet.

218
00:12:04,657 --> 00:12:07,560
I know one thing, he's nuts.

219
00:12:11,163 --> 00:12:14,633
I've seen one or
two like him before.

220
00:12:14,667 --> 00:12:16,469
Stubborn kids who'd rather die,

221
00:12:16,502 --> 00:12:20,673
than have to turn away from
a fight, once it's started.

222
00:12:20,740 --> 00:12:22,174
He'll stay.

223
00:12:22,241 --> 00:12:24,777
That's for sure.

224
00:12:24,810 --> 00:12:25,745
I'm glad he's with us,

225
00:12:25,745 --> 00:12:28,581
'cause guys like that
are hell to fight.

226
00:12:31,150 --> 00:12:34,086
[ZEFF] I don't care
if he wins or loses,

227
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:38,424
I consider it an honor,
just to be able to watch him.

228
00:12:41,527 --> 00:12:42,528
[SANJI gasps]

229
00:13:16,896 --> 00:13:17,730
[PATTY]
Hey, man!

230
00:13:17,797 --> 00:13:18,964
[CARNE]
You all right?

231
00:13:18,998 --> 00:13:20,032
Try to breathe.

232
00:13:20,065 --> 00:13:21,967
You need a little fresh air.

233
00:13:22,001 --> 00:13:25,171
You want a pillow
or maybe some water?

234
00:13:25,204 --> 00:13:26,505
Speak!

235
00:13:26,539 --> 00:13:30,009
[labored breathing]

236
00:13:30,042 --> 00:13:31,143
This is bad.

237
00:13:31,177 --> 00:13:32,077
You know what?

238
00:13:32,144 --> 00:13:34,046
I make a great banana pudding.
Want some?

239
00:13:34,079 --> 00:13:36,148
You idiot, we don't want
him to choke to death

240
00:13:36,148 --> 00:13:37,650
on any of your
culinary disasters!

241
00:13:37,683 --> 00:13:39,018
Better that, than
the trots he'd get

242
00:13:39,051 --> 00:13:41,153
from choking down one of
your raunchy meat pies!

243
00:13:41,187 --> 00:13:43,255
The reason I won't feed
him one of my meat pies,

244
00:13:43,322 --> 00:13:44,824
is because after one bite,

245
00:13:44,857 --> 00:13:47,226
he'd think he'd died
and gone to heaven!

246
00:13:47,259 --> 00:13:48,093
[BOTH yelling]

247
00:13:48,160 --> 00:13:49,829
Don't die yet!

248
00:13:49,829 --> 00:13:51,530
Come on, breathe more!

249
00:13:51,564 --> 00:13:53,165
You're not really dead,
you're not really dead,

250
00:13:53,199 --> 00:13:55,167
you're not really dead,
