An exploding spear?

304
00:16:21,313 --> 00:16:22,014
Now what?

305
00:16:22,047 --> 00:16:25,250
You gonna try
to hide from me?

306
00:16:25,317 --> 00:16:26,685
All right then, boy.

307
00:16:26,719 --> 00:16:28,687
